Home


Business travel services

Group & Meeting Travel 



Group & Meeting Travel 



Group products
We offer group fares and amenities for 10 or more people traveling together to a common destination as well as special pricing for leisure, incentive and company meeting travel.




Leisure groups 
This content can be expanded


From family reunions to sports teams, we offer guaranteed group fares for 10 or more traveling together to the same destination.
Group fares 
If your group is traveling together to any American or oneworld® destination, you can get a guaranteed fare and block space up to 11 months in advance. We also provide additional flexibility by offering these features:

One free name change per ticket up to 48 hours prior to departure 
Saturday-night or minimum stay not required  
Names and ticketing vary by destination 



										Request a proposal
										
											







Company meetings
This content can be expanded


Need assistance with special fares for your company meeting?
Zone fares
For association or company meetings of 10 or more, we’ll guarantee fares from various geographical zones of departure to your destination. Zone fares are ideal for mid-week meetings as a Saturday-night stay is not required, and they’re valid for travel originating in the United States or Canada to:

North America
Europe
Caribbean
Latin America 
Pacific



										Request a proposal
										
											







Group incentive travel 
This content can be expanded


Select the destination for your top sales individuals, and we'll get them there with a program tailored to the incentive market. Plus, we provide future-date pricing which allows you to forecast your travel expenses.
Zone fares
For incentive travel of 10 or more, we’ll guarantee fares from various geographical zones of departure to your destination. Zone fares are ideal for mid-week meetings as a Saturday-night stay is not required, and they’re valid for travel originating in the United States or Canada to:

North America
Europe
Caribbean
Latin America
Pacific



										Request a proposal
										
											


Group fares
Groups traveling together to any American or oneworld® destination can get a guaranteed fare and block space up to 11 months in advance. We also provide additional flexibility by offering these features:

One free name change per ticket up to 48 hours prior to departure 
Saturday-night or minimum stay not required 
Names and ticketing vary by destination 



										Request a proposal
										
											





Additional amenities
Avoid long lines with self-service check-in 
If you’re traveling in a group of 10 or more passengers booked in a single reservation, you can check in individually with our self-service machines.


										Learn more about self-service check-in
										
											


Special rental car rates 
American Airlines Group & Meeting Travel has a preferred partnership with Avis® and Budget® to help you save further on travel. Now, when you contract your group or meeting through American Airlines, your attendees will receive Avis or Budget rental cars at reduced rates.


Contact us
To learn how we can assist with your group or meeting travel, please submit your request online or contact us by phone or email.
Online


										Request a proposal
										
											


